Title: Series: Varii capricci e paesi
Description: Landscape with at centre a woman cradling a child on a donkey that is drinking from a stream and held on a leash by her husband; at left a shepherd figure kneeling behind a tree watches them, and further left another shepherd hurries a cow and lambs across a bridge, possibly representing the flight into Egypt Etching
Curator's comments: For comment on the set see 1859,0611.271.*.
Associated names: Associated with: Antonio Maria Zanetti I
